{
  "id": "69f5988e4bc6f097b4f5d4bc",
  "title": "あいまい文を集めて鑑賞する本とか作りたい",
  "created": 1777703056,
  "updated": 1777775637,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f5988e4bc6f097b4f5d4bc",
      "text": "あいまい文を集めて鑑賞する本とか作りたい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527508",
      "text": "from [2026/04/29]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527509",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777704969
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f000000000052750a",
      "text": "[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f000000000052750b",
      "text": " あいまい文を集めて鑑賞する本とか作りたいかもしれない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f000000000052750c",
      "text": "\t昨日の「[メタ認知が終わっている]」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777775586
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f000000000052750d",
      "text": "\t厳密にはあいまい文ではないかもしれない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f000000000052750e",
      "text": "\t想定しているのは、「頭が赤い魚を食べる猫」みたいなやつ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f000000000052750f",
      "text": "\t統語論的にあいまい文になるやつ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527510",
      "text": "\tしかし、語用論的、意味論的にあいまい文になるやつを収集したって良い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527511",
      "text": "\t俺はウエハース[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527512",
      "text": "\t\t字義通り読むと変だが文脈的には意味が通る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527513",
      "text": "\t\tウエハース文だ！[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527514",
      "text": "\t\tもしかして：[うなぎ文]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527515",
      "text": "\t弁慶がなぎなたをもってな……[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527516",
      "text": "\t\t区切り位置がズレて新名詞が類推されるもの",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527517",
      "text": "\t\t[ぎなた読み]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527518",
      "text": "\t\tこの読み方の事例がなぎなたなの意味がわからんよな[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f0000000000527519",
      "text": "\t\t　もっといい例があるのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f000000000052751a",
      "text": "\t\t　「[ここではきものをぬいでください]」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777775602
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6b3f90000000000bb7ae0",
      "text": "\t\tこれも[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777775609,
      "updated": 1777775637
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6b40f0000000000bb7ae1",
      "text": "\t\t\tトイレは座ってするよ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777775631,
      "updated": 1777775633
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6b4100000000000bb7ae2",
      "text": "\t\t\tうにお願いします",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777775633,
      "updated": 1777775633
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5988f000000000052751b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703056,
      "updated": 1777703056
    }
  ]
}